{"tid":886974,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"15K LIST 求評","createTime":"2018-11-02T13:46:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-03T03:53:16.000Z","uid":32248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"4aedc041ca9d974f4da708d5d5342b836a38173b","tid":886974,"uid":32248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T13:46:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RZnnrRF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRZnnrRF.jpg&h=22251fa8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n想聖誕後, 出雙糧砌機, 預算15k-16k 左右(含WINDWOS 10) <br />\n本人新機9成時間用黎打機(主要打3D online game或 overwatch, 極小打單機/大作) <br />\n另外 多開android 模擬器, 多開網頁, 直播, 即時通訊軟件 <br />\n<br />\n想請教各位, 以上條list ok嗎? <br />\n1, 塊底板, 如果想小小地超頻, 安唔安全, 夠唔夠力? 如果唔ok 的話, 有冇其他牌子/型號推介? <br />\n2, 同上, 火牛用750w , 安唔安全, 夠唔夠力? <br />\n3, ram 方面 夾唔夾到粒2700x ? 我聽聞amd cpu 要夾ram 和 佢果條寫住 intel ? <br />\n4, 散熱方面, 小小地超, 用以上的風冷ok嗎? 又或者有冇其他牌子推介下? 聽聞貓頭鷹好d? 但顏色就... <br />\n5, 機箱方面, 花多眼亂, 真係唔知點揀好, 但想用散熱好小小+有側透的(因為放角位 平時小d 空氣流動), 求推介 <br />\n<br />\n暫時諗到咁多, 諗到再問, 雖然早1個月, 但係想做定功課 <br />\n唔該晒 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c82ea5a68d16714cc3cf64f5f0e1b4ef47460daf","tid":886974,"uid":32248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T22:49:24.000Z","msg":"抐 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a98dd1477d4baa1064ee9d9bb7f48f8f9664721a","tid":886974,"uid":79245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T23:32:11.000Z","msg":"不要wd<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0db1b5ff8603e924bba81df27198de3765fbc75","tid":886974,"uid":79245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T23:34:23.000Z","msg":"貓扇硬件po 個個推神扇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   自己爬下文  都係加多兩百姐  用佢實冇死"},{"pid":"4a5c63ae1724290414c507664d90e849d278173b","tid":886974,"uid":58